title: Cross Country: Vineland claims team title
text: Cross Country: Vineland claims team title Buy Photo Vineland 3rd place finisher Zach Carbonara, bottom, celebrates with teammate and 1st place finisher Harrison Mayo as Cumberland County College hosts the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at in Vineland. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer Fullscreen Buy Photo Vineland's Ventrelle Smith en route, finishing 11th at the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at Cumberland County College in Vineland. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer Fullscreen Buy Photo Vineland's Harrison Mayo crosses the finish line at the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at Cumberland County College in Vineland. Mayo finished 1st for the boys with a time of 17:27.59. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer Fullscreen Buy Photo Cumberland Regional's Mike Girock, front, catches his breath at the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at Cumberland County College in Vineland. Girock finished 20th at 19:44.50. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer Fullscreen Buy Photo Millville's McKenzie Springsteadah eyes the finish line as she takes 1st place for the girls at the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at Cumberland County College in Vineland. Her final time was 21:09.00. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer Fullscreen Buy Photo Cumberland Regional's Sara Lowe crosses the finish line at the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at Cumberland County College in Vineland. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer Fullscreen Buy Photo Vineland's Harrison Mayo gets out ahead of everyone at the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at Cumberland County College in Vineland. Mayo finished 1st for the boys with a time of 17:27.59. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer Fullscreen Buy Photo The boys take off at the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at Cumberland County College in Vineland. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer Fullscreen Buy Photo Vineland's Zach Carbonara takes 3rd with a time of 17:48.72 as Cumberland County College hosts the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at in Vineland. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer Fullscreen Buy Photo Vineland's Zyair Dennis turns a corner at the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at Cumberland County College in Vineland. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer Fullscreen Buy Photo Vineland's Iebette Cruz-Lopez takes 8th place at the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at Cumberland County College in Vineland. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer Fullscreen Buy Photo A runner from Bridgeton High School stays on path at the Cumberland County Cross Country Championships Thursday, Oct. 22 at Cumberland County College in Vineland. Joe Lamberti/Staff Photographer
